Package com.atakmap.android.navigation.models

Class NavButtonModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.atakmap.android.navigation.models.NavButtonModel
  • public class NavButtonModel
extends java.lang.Object
    Model for use with NavButton It's recommend to use NavButtonModel.Builder for creation. When an aspect of the model is changed, it is important to call NavButtonManager.getInstance().notifyModelChanged not notify all users of the model.

        image - an image to show in a unselected state
        selectedImage - an image to show in a selected state
